{
  "id": "RAW_c65e949a",
  "title": "实测 5 万元的苹果 AIPC，比我们想象的还要出色｜M5 Max MacBook Pro 评测",
  "url": "https://www.ifanr.com/1657403?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=",
  "date": "2026-03-10 13:55:33",
  "author": "马扶摇",
  "siteName": "爱范儿",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>如果有 5 万块钱的预算，用来配一台个人电脑，你会怎么选？</p>\n  <p>放在以前，你可能会把预算的大头放在显卡上——毕竟无论是「玩游戏」还是「下班玩游戏」，有个强悍的 GPU 总归不是一件坏事。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657404\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-new-gpu-lol.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1042\" height=\"630\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-new-gpu-lol.jpg!720 1042w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-new-gpu-lol-360x218.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-new-gpu-lol-768x464.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-new-gpu-lol-1024x619.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1042px) 100vw, 1042px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜网络</span></p>\n  <p>可如今，这个问题变得复杂起来。</p>\n  <p>以往在 CPU、GPU、主板、内存、硬盘、外设之间有序分布的预算，突然被内存这头「吞金巨兽」打乱。</p>\n  <p>这下无论计划用电脑做什么，你都会碰到<strong>顾此失彼</strong>的问题——</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p>大内存、大显存、大硬盘每个都不能缺，但每个都会让钱包滴血。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p>而在内存乱潮中异军突起的 Mac，恰恰就是上面那个问题的最佳解决方案。</p>\n  <h2>迄今最强的 AI Mac</h2>\n  <p>刚刚过去的春季发布会上，苹果如期带来了 M5 MacBook Pro 的升级版机型，以及配套的 M5 Pro 和 M5 Max 处理器。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657405\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-mbp-live.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"4032\" height=\"3024\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-mbp-live.jpg!720 4032w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-mbp-live-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-mbp-live-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-mbp-live-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 4032px) 100vw, 4032px\"></p>\n  <p>作为 Apple Silicon 全面更新台积电 3nm N3P 工艺的结果，两款新处理器在规格上的确没有让我们失望。</p>\n  <p>其中，M5 Pro 有 15+16 和 18+20 核两种规模，均搭载了去年 M5 上的神经网络加速器，也就是那个「苹果版的 Tensor Core」。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657406\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-neural-core.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1960\" height=\"1306\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-neural-core.jpg!720 1960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-neural-core-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-neural-core-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-neural-core-1024x682.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1960px) 100vw, 1960px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Apple</span></p>\n  <p>M5 Max 本次则有 18+32 和 18+40 核可选，以及 16 核神经网络加速器。仅从处理器规模上看，M5 Pro 与 M5 Max 毫无疑问都是 <strong>GPU 优先</strong>的。</p>\n  <p>这种倾向也体现在了新处理器的微架构设计上。</p>\n  <p>目前，所有 M5 系列的处理器均换装了 LPDDR5X 9600 统一内存，根据苹果的介绍，M5 Pro 的最大内存带宽为 307GB/s，M5 Max 则有 <strong>614GB/s</strong>：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657407\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-M5-family.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1564\" height=\"748\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-M5-family.png!720 1564w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-M5-family-360x172.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-M5-family-768x367.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-M5-family-1024x490.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1564px) 100vw, 1564px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Apple</span></p>\n  <p>既然 M5 Pro 和 M5 Max 标配 18 核 CPU，那么导致内存带宽不同的原因大概率就在 GPU 规格上。</p>\n  <p>结合发布前的预测，这种差异侧面说明了 <strong>M5 系列的内存控制器很有可能是设置在 GPU 核心簇上的</strong>。</p>\n  <p>这种策略和爱范儿去年参访英特尔工厂时看到的 Panther Lake 架构心有灵犀：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657408\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-panther-lake.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"4032\" height=\"3024\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-panther-lake.jpg!720 4032w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-panther-lake-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-panther-lake-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-panther-lake-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 4032px) 100vw, 4032px\"></p>\n  <p>这样做的好处很明显——将 GPU 与内存控制器靠近，可以非常有效地缓解内存数据的核间通讯的延迟，变相提升 GPU 效率。</p>\n  <p>而速度更快、VRAM 更大的 GPU 最擅长什么呢？当然是本地 AI 应用了。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657409\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-msty-deepseek.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-msty-deepseek.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-msty-deepseek-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-msty-deepseek-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-msty-deepseek-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>这也是本次苹果在官网页面上非常高频提及「AI」的原因之一。</p>\n  <p>就拿爱范儿这台 14 寸 MacBook Pro 样机来说，我们收到的是今年最顶规的 40 核 GPU M5 Max 版本，搭配 128GB 统一内存和 8TB 硬盘，一台超过 5.5 万元的性能怪兽。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657410\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-mbp-soc-mosaic.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-mbp-soc-mosaic.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-mbp-soc-mosaic-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-mbp-soc-mosaic-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-mbp-soc-mosaic-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>一般来说，当我们用 Windows PC 跑本地模型的时候，最大的瓶颈往往不是卖出天价的「主板内存」，而是显卡内部的 VRAM 显存。</p>\n  <p>而苹果统一内存的最大优势，就在于它可以被 GPU 直接调用。</p>\n  <p>比如我们这台 128GB M5 Max 评测机，理论上甚至可以为 GPU 提供接近 100GB 的显存空间：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657411\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-mbp-ram-usage-1.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-mbp-ram-usage-1.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-mbp-ram-usage-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-mbp-ram-usage-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-mbp-ram-usage-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>既然有了这么充裕的内存，我们当然要按照苹果宣传的那样，狠狠运行一下那些以前跑不了的大规模本地 AI 模型了。</p>\n  <p>在 llmfit 中可以看到：<strong>一块 128GB 的 M5 Max，对于所有不超过 125b 的模型都可以「顺跑」(perfect)。</strong></p>\n  <p>直到 220b 以上的 MiniMax M2.5、Qwen3 和 DeepSeek v2.5 等等，才会变成「勉强能跑」(marginal)：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657412\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-M5-max-in-llmfit.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3246\" height=\"2122\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-M5-max-in-llmfit.png!720 3246w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-M5-max-in-llmfit-360x235.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-M5-max-in-llmfit-768x502.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-M5-max-in-llmfit-1024x669.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3246px) 100vw, 3246px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ M5 Max 128GB</span></p>\n  <p>相比之下，32GB 内存的 M1 Max 用 llmfit 查一下，<strong>最多也就只能跑一跑 2 或 4bit 量化 35b 左右的模型了</strong>：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657413\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-M1-Max-in-llmtest.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3686\" height=\"2366\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-M1-Max-in-llmtest.png!720 3686w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-M1-Max-in-llmtest-360x231.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-M1-Max-in-llmtest-768x493.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-M1-Max-in-llmtest-1024x657.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3686px) 100vw, 3686px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ M1 Max 32GB</span></p>\n  <p>考虑到部署的便捷程度，以及上下文理解的空间，我们选择通过 LM Studio 测试 qwen3.5-35b-a3b，以及支持 MLX 的 qwen3-next-80b，<strong>两者均为 8-bit 量化的 MoE 模型</strong>：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657414\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-lm-studio-loader.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1602\" height=\"614\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-lm-studio-loader.png!720 1602w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-lm-studio-loader-360x138.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-lm-studio-loader-768x294.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-lm-studio-loader-1024x392.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1602px) 100vw, 1602px\"></p>\n  <p>对于 qwen3.5-35b-a3b 这种「总量和推理数量都不大」的 MoE 模型来说，M5 Max 经常是还<strong>没来得及热起来</strong>就跑完了：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657415\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-qwen35b.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3248\" height=\"2122\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-qwen35b.png!720 3248w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-qwen35b-360x235.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-qwen35b-768x502.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-qwen35b-1024x669.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3248px) 100vw, 3248px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ qwen3.5-35b-a3b</span></p>\n  <p>即使面对接近 3000 字的原文材料，在手动拉满模型 token 上限之后，M5 Max 在每一轮重写和仿写中的<strong>首词元响应速度都在 1.7 秒左右</strong>，即 TTFT 约 1.7s、TPOT 约 65tps，累计思考和撰写的字数近万也没有溢出。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657416\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-qwen35b_2.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3248\" height=\"2122\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-qwen35b_2.png!720 3248w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-qwen35b_2-360x235.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-qwen35b_2-768x502.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-qwen35b_2-1024x669.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3248px) 100vw, 3248px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ qwen3.5-35b-a3b</span></p>\n  <p>而有 MLX 优化、8-bit 量化且参数量更大的 qwen3-next-80b 在 M5 Max 上更是如虎添翼。</p>\n  <p>虽然需要忽略内存警告手动加载接近 80GB 的模型，但是运行效果的确非同凡响：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><strong>在 qwen3.5-35b-a3b 中需要思考近 30 秒的相同提示词，输给 qwen3-next-80b 则是接近秒出，TTFT 约 3s、TPOT 约 72tps。</strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657417\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-qwen3next.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3248\" height=\"2122\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-qwen3next.png!720 3248w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-qwen3next-360x235.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-qwen3next-768x502.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-qwen3next-1024x669.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3248px) 100vw, 3248px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ qwen3-next-80b</span></p>\n  <p>这一方面是因为 80b 的参数相比 3b 活跃参数本来就够大，更因为这是基于<strong>苹果开源的 MLX 框架</strong>优化的版本，可以最大发挥出 Apple Silicon 的优势。</p>\n  <p>除了 MoE 模型之外，M5 Max 面对类似 Llama 3.3 这样的稠密模型的表现怎么样呢？</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657418\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-Llama.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2752\" height=\"1536\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-Llama.jpeg!720 2752w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-Llama-360x201.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-Llama-768x429.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-Llama-1024x572.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2752px) 100vw, 2752px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Tom’s Guide</span></p>\n  <p>尽管 8-bit 量化的 Llama 3.3 70b 模型体积只有约 75GB，但 128k 上下文所需的巨大 KV cache 还是会溢出，导致 LM Studio 无法加载。</p>\n  <p>换成体积更小的 <strong>Llama 3.3 70b Q4_K_M</strong> 之后 M5 Max 终于可以正常加载了，执行上述提示词后系统负载约为 95GB，生成速度 9.95 token/s：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657419\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-llama70b.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3248\" height=\"2122\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-llama70b.png!720 3248w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-llama70b-360x235.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-llama70b-768x502.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-llama70b-1024x669.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3248px) 100vw, 3248px\"></p>\n  <p>换句话说，<strong>在面对类似规模的稠密模型的时候，还是需要更大内存的 M3 Ultra 上场</strong>。</p>\n  <p>不过我们本次在 M5 Max 上观测到的最大占用，反而不是稠密的 Llama 3.3，而是跑在 Msty Studio 里面的 deepseeek-r1：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657420\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-mbp-max-ram-usage.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-mbp-max-ram-usage.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-mbp-max-ram-usage-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-mbp-max-ram-usage-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-mbp-max-ram-usage-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>在 Msty Studio 中，我们加载了一个 75GB 的 deepseek-r1 70b-llama-distill-q8_0，<strong>花两分钟占用 122GB 内存</strong>给你写了首俳句：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657421\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-msty-deepseek-lame.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3024\" height=\"1964\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-msty-deepseek-lame.png!720 3024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-msty-deepseek-lame-360x234.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-msty-deepseek-lame-768x499.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-msty-deepseek-lame-1024x665.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3024px) 100vw, 3024px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ deepseek-r1 70b-llama-distill-q8_0</span></p>\n  <p>这还仅仅是本地语言类模型的成绩，即使在一些传统性能项目中，M5 Max 的表现同样没有让我们失望。</p>\n  <p>在 Cinebench 2026 中，<strong>M5 Max 最高跑出了 GPU 79295 分的成绩</strong>，相比 M4 Max 提升了超过 15%，和目前规模最大的 M3 Ultra 仅差 5% 左右。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657422\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/19-cinebench-gpu.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3248\" height=\"2122\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/19-cinebench-gpu.png!720 3248w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/19-cinebench-gpu-360x235.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/19-cinebench-gpu-768x502.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/19-cinebench-gpu-1024x669.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3248px) 100vw, 3248px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 连续烤机后下降到了 7.7 万分左右</span></p>\n  <p>而这样的成绩放到游戏中是什么样呢？</p>\n  <p>我们按照与去年评测标准版 M5 时相同的参数，重新在 M5 Max 上玩了一会《赛博朋克 2077》。</p>\n  <p>在使用默认「for this mac」预设时，M5 Max 可以稳定在 59 帧左右，<strong>相比标准版 M5 不仅预设分辨率更高、细节更多，帧率更是直接翻倍</strong>：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657424\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/20-test-2077.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3024\" height=\"2519\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/20-test-2077.jpg!720 3024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/20-test-2077-360x300.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/20-test-2077-768x640.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/20-test-2077-1024x853.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3024px) 100vw, 3024px\"></p>\n  <p>在手动优化一下设置（高细节 1.5K 光追 FSR MetalFX 超分和帧生成）之后，M5 Max 则可以在风扇拉满的情况下稳定住密集场景 50～60 帧——</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657425\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/21-dogtown-walk.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"623\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/21-dogtown-walk.gif 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/21-dogtown-walk-360x234.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/21-dogtown-walk-768x498.gif 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"></p>\n  <p>这个成绩距离游戏本当然差不少，但 2077 本来就是个非常庞大的游戏，M5 Max 能够在不插电的 14 寸机身里面跑出这样的效果，还是很让人惊喜的。</p>\n  <p>至于其他体量更小、优化更好的游戏，比如《控制：终极合辑》、《逃离鸭科夫》等等，只要不乱改设置，M5 Max 基本都可以稳住 60 帧一根线。</p>\n  <p>无论是 AI 工作流，还是打游戏，<strong>这款 M5 Max 芯片的 MacBook Pro，是一只毫无疑问的澎湃猛兽</strong>。</p>\n  <h2>迄今最好的苹果屏幕</h2>\n  <p>除了 M5 Pro/Max 之外，今年春季发布会上的另一个「Pro 级」新品则是千呼万唤始出来的新一代 Studio Display。</p>\n  <p>更具体一点说，是新款 Studio Display 和 Studio Display XDR。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657426\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-XDR-with-MBP.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"4032\" height=\"3024\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-XDR-with-MBP.jpg!720 4032w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-XDR-with-MBP-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-XDR-with-MBP-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/22-XDR-with-MBP-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 4032px) 100vw, 4032px\"></p>\n  <p>在 Pro Display XDR 下架之后，Studio Display XDR 接过了它的衣钵，凭借着 24,999 的起售价成为了目前苹果专业级显示器的门面担当。</p>\n  <p>而我们在上手 Studio Display XDR 之后的初体验也和 Apple 活动现场一致：</p>\n  <p><strong>屏幕面积缩小的影响并不明显，反而是 ProMotion 从第一秒就抓住了我们的目光——</strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657427\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/23-xdr-promotion.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/23-xdr-promotion.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/23-xdr-promotion-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/23-xdr-promotion-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/23-xdr-promotion-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>得益于一块 2304 分区的 mini-LED 面板，以及 1000 尼特峰值 SDR 亮度、2000 尼特峰值 HDR 亮度，说它「不抓人眼球」是不可能的。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657428\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/24-xdr-hue-glow.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/24-xdr-hue-glow.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/24-xdr-hue-glow-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/24-xdr-hue-glow-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/24-xdr-hue-glow-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ mini-LED 的光晕现象只在非常极限的情况下可见</span></p>\n  <p>在「老生常谈」的广色域 HDR 内容创作之外，Studio Display XDR 当然也是影音娱乐的一把好手。</p>\n  <p>尤其是当你手头有一些支持 HDR 效果的「欧美大片」的话，用 MacBook Pro 搭配 Studio Display XDR 的体验，在目前的苹果产品线中是无出其右的：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657429\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/25-xdr-watching-1.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/25-xdr-watching-1.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/25-xdr-watching-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/25-xdr-watching-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/25-xdr-watching-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>而相同的评价对于今年的新款 Studio Display 同样适用。</p>\n  <p>实际上，除了 ProMotion、峰值亮度和充电功率之外，Studio Display 在屏幕面板素质方面，完全可以看齐新的 Studio Display XDR ——</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657430\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/26-xdr-watching-2.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/26-xdr-watching-2.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/26-xdr-watching-2-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/26-xdr-watching-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/26-xdr-watching-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>毕竟苹果事先打好了招呼：<strong>5K 120Hz 可不是随便什么处理器都能带动的，如果你的 Mac 使用的是 M1 全系、M2 或 M3 标准版的话，插上 Studio Display XDR 最高只能以 60Hz 显示。</strong></p>\n  <p>这也符合我们拿到 Studio Display XDR 的体验结果。</p>\n  <p>甚至如果你的 macOS 版本太老，即使插上显示器能够充电，也是无法输出画面的。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657431\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/27-xdr-general-2.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/27-xdr-general-2.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/27-xdr-general-2-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/27-xdr-general-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/27-xdr-general-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>有意思的是，爱范儿在发布会现场和苹果的工作人员交流时，他们提到：<strong>两款显示器都搭载了 iPhone 的 SoC 芯片</strong>。</p>\n  <p>而外媒 MacRumors 通过解包两款新显示器的固件更新代码，发现苹果分别为两款新显示器装上了 A19 和 A19 Pro 处理器——</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657432\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/28-xdr-top.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/28-xdr-top.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/28-xdr-top-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/28-xdr-top-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/28-xdr-top-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>不出意料，这是为了 5K 画面解码、背光控制、Center Stage 摄像头以及其他显示器功能准备的。</p>\n  <p>但这也让苹果的「处理器笑话」越来越多了：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><strong>2026 年刚开头，你就可以买到 M5 芯片的 iPad Pro、A18 Pro 芯片的 MacBook Neo，以及 A19 Pro 芯片的显示器。</strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p>总的来说，今年的 Studio Display XDR 是一次非常及时的更新。</p>\n  <p>它最重要的意义，在于补全了苹果专业级产品线中 ProMotion 的缺口，也是让产品联动的体验更加无缝。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657433\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/29-ensemble.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/29-ensemble.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/29-ensemble-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/29-ensemble-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/29-ensemble-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <h2>当苹果开始谈论 AI</h2>\n  <p>这次的春季发布会上，苹果除了改变之前的发布模式之外，也开始大大方方地谈论起了 AI ——</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657434\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/30-official-site.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3680\" height=\"2392\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/30-official-site.png!720 3680w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/30-official-site-360x234.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/30-official-site-768x499.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/30-official-site-1024x666.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3680px) 100vw, 3680px\"></p>\n  <p>这次的 AI 不是一鸽再鸽的 Apple Intelligence，也不是苹果曾经反复强调的 Machine Learning，就是简单直白的<strong>通用人工智能</strong>。</p>\n  <p>而从目前的产品表现来看，当苹果开始谈论 AI，它确实是准备好了。</p>\n  <p>早在苹果 2020 年转向 Apple Silicon 与统一内存架构时，它大概率没有想到如今的 AI 模型需求大爆发，以及随之而来的内存危机。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657435\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/31-first-gen-unified-memory.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1087\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/31-first-gen-unified-memory.jpeg!720 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/31-first-gen-unified-memory-360x204.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/31-first-gen-unified-memory-768x435.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/31-first-gen-unified-memory-1024x580.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"></p>\n  <p>最直白的例子，莫过于这块 M5 Max 上的 128GB 统一内存：</p>\n  <ul>\n   <li>如果只看消费级 DDR5 6400 内存，想要买足 128GB 的确不是难事，所需开销<strong>仅仅一万元</strong>左右，但无论如何也达不到 614GB/s 的带宽。</li>\n   <li>如果想要用显卡凑够 128GB 的 VRAM，在专业卡买不到的前提下，你需要买<strong>整整五块 RTX 5090D</strong>，这还是忽略显卡间通讯延迟之后的结果。</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>这种时候，有本地 AI 需求的小型企业团队、个人开发者、AI 从业者等等就会陷入两难的境地：</p>\n  <p><strong>要么用有限的预算，在搭建 PC 时将预算分割到内存、显卡、CPU、硬盘等等上面，稀释整体的计算性能。</strong></p>\n  <p><strong>要么咬紧牙关加预算，投入几十乃至上百万元，进入自构服务器的领域。</strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657436\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/32-small-company-server.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"807\" height=\"537\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/32-small-company-server.jpeg!720 807w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/32-small-company-server-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/32-small-company-server-768x511.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 807px) 100vw, 807px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Servermall</span></p>\n  <p>这时，一台不到 6 万元，自带 128GB 高带宽内存、顶级 HDR 屏幕和扬声器，以及 8TB 硬盘的 MacBook Pro，<strong>反而变成了个人和工作室用户的终极性价比之选</strong>。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657437\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/33-mbp-side-port.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3504\" height=\"2336\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/33-mbp-side-port.jpg!720 3504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/33-mbp-side-port-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/33-mbp-side-port-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/33-mbp-side-port-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3504px) 100vw, 3504px\"></p>\n  <p>甚至如果你用不到上面那些「外设」，或者本地 AI 需求不高的话，还可以退而求其次选择 Mac Studio 或者 Mac mini ——</p>\n  <p>而后者已经在刚刚的「龙虾潮」中迎来了一波自己的春天。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657438\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/34-mac-server-rack.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"796\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/34-mac-server-rack.jpeg!720 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/34-mac-server-rack-360x239.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/34-mac-server-rack-768x509.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/34-mac-server-rack-1024x679.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Apple Must</span></p>\n  <p>虽然 Apple Intelligence 引人发笑，但 Apple Silicon 和统一内存在这个「大 AI 时代」的潜力，才只露出冰山一角。</p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深入评测了 M5 Max MacBook Pro 在本地 AI 任务中的表现，强调统一内存架构在运行大参数模型方面的独特优势与性价比。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深入评测了 M5 Max MacBook Pro 在本地 AI 任务中的表现，强调统一内存架构在运行大参数模型方面的独特优势与性价比。",
  "summary": "文章对顶配版 M5 Max MacBook Pro（128GB 统一内存）进行了深度实测。核心聚焦于其作为“AI PC”的实战能力，详细分析了 M5 系列芯片在台积电 3nm N3P 工艺下的架构改进，特别是 M5 Max 达到的 614GB/s 极高内存带宽。通过运行 Qwen 3.5、Llama 3.3 和 DeepSeek-R1 等主流大模型，验证了统一内存作为超大显存（VRAM）在处理 125B 以上参数模型时的绝对优势。此外，评测还涵盖了新款 Studio Display XDR 的显示素质及 M5 Max 在 3A 游戏中的表现，认为其已成为 AI 开发者和小型工作室的终极生产力工具。",
